nce it implements `Into<Text>`, so the refactored `render_status` function returning lines instead of a joined string will work seamlessly. The order of status messages stays the same—just collected as lines instead of concatenated.\n\nNow I'm implementing the changes, keeping in mind that `Style` is `Copy` in ratatui, so cloning theme fields is straightforward, and `Span::styled()` with formatted strings handles the `'static` lifetime requirement naturally.\n\nWriting the refactored code... I'll use the Edit tool.\n\nThe file structure I need to change:\n\n**1. Imports** - add Color, Span\nLine 13: `use ratatui::style::{Modifier, Style};`\n→ `use ratatui::style::{Color, Modifier, Style};`\nLine 14: `use ratatui::text::Line;`\n→ `use ratatui::text::{Line, Span};`\n\n**2. After line 31 (end of TuiArgs)**, add ColorSupport, Theme, TerminalCapability types\n\n**3. Change `pub async fn run(...)` to check terminal capability**\n\n**4. After TuiArgs but before run(), add the new types**\n\n**5. In AppState struct**, add `theme: Theme` field\n\n**6. Replace `#[derive(Default)]` on AppState with manual impl**\n\n**7. In render_conversation**, add styled spans\n\n**8. In render_status**, change to return Vec<Line<'static>>\n\n**9. In render_worker_list**, add styled spans for badges and selected marker\n\n**10. In draw_ui**, use theme for block title styles and input title hints\n\n**11. Update error_status handling...","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":4013,"cache_read_input_tokens":55949,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":4013},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"b35f4001-d232-4171-b853-fb6a26d102e1","uuid":"63c746bf-6ed4-4f25-98d7-9923b63baae7"}
