{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01NbdWHrM7qsZQKSpk3h3qv1","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_013ZM42yhGJ1XxcCyYJ9m2s3","name":"Bash","input":{"command":"git add crates/cli/src/cmd/tui.rs crates/cli/Cargo.toml crates/config/src/schema.rs crates/bootstrap/src/lib.rs && git commit -m \"$(cat <<'EOF'\nfeat: US-034 - Ratatui theming, accessibility, and fallback policy\n\n- Add TuiConfig to config schema with theme field (default/high_contrast/no_color)\n- Expose tui_theme() helper in ccode_bootstrap to route config access cleanly\n- Implement Theme struct with three variants: default (16-color), high_contrast\n  (bold+bright), no_color (modifiers only, no fg colors)\n- Detect NO_COLOR env var and TERM=dumb to auto-select no_color theme\n- Terminal capability probe: attempt raw_mode; fall back to standard REPL\n  (repl::run) when terminal is unsupported (TERM=dumb, non-interactive pipes)\n- Apply themed Style spans across conversation, status, and worker panels\n- Rename render_status() to render_status_lines() returning Vec<Line> with\n  styled [*] info and [!] error non-color prefix indicators\n- Add [Enter/Shift+Enter/Ctrl+C/PgUp/PgDn] key hints to Input pane title\n- Embed key action hints in Tool Approval modal title (non-color accessible)\n- Panic hook and TerminalGuard RAII already in place; confirmed intact\n- Add 9 new tests covering theme variants, color detection, non-color\n  accessibility markers, and key hints\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Sonnet 4.6 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>\nEOF\n)\"","timeout":30000},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":216,"cache_read_input_tokens":104808,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":216},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_t